能力應付重建香港既需要<br />\n<br />\n要有一班人合組左個新政府，先有本錢take over政權"},{"pid":"3761732c52ceb85f938b9d352769d69f26e4dc59","tid":2023861,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9beaeee62c071dbb329f41717bab4bc6c525926d","tid":2023861,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"大台不了"},{"pid":"3d2a13ce670abad69fe937c7004a41cd81738b08","tid":2023861,"uid":58164,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"其實繼續係本土已經冇咩發展空間....<br />\n係海外都係一個選擇...."},{"pid":"e517c88f5adab37a76d2b10b5963bfb493b343bf","tid":2023861,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"同時要培訓人材"},{"pid":"8cacfa44405256865476d74e8d55d16a3b8825af","tid":2023861,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3d2a13ce670abad69fe937c7004a41cd81738b08","tid":2023861,"uid":58164,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"其實繼續係本土已經冇咩發展空間....<br />\n係海外都係一個選擇...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"其實真 要考慮海外建軍"},{"pid":"30abc696be4f3d7fadfb70e53dabd599707f3850","tid":2023861,"uid":68125,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9beaeee62c071dbb329f41717bab4bc6c525926d","tid":2023861,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"大台不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"問題係喺香港被重重打壓，都要諗其他可能方法<br />\n而唔係叫衝衝子捱打同被自殺"},{"pid":"e330d5fd06669e7f98a3696bfb6d1b6b2cedc7d5","tid":2023861,"uid":43751,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e517c88f5adab37a76d2b10b5963bfb493b343bf","tid":2023861,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1